        <mxCell id="current" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EFF6FF;strokeColor=#3B82F6;align=left;spacingLeft=18;fontSize=15" value="当前已完成&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• V3.5：Application Adaptation Layer baseline&lt;br&gt;• V3.6：Workflow Runtime Contract + Dummy Pipeline E2E&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-0/A/A2：UI contract、Workflow Studio shell、真实 BFF read/event bridge&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-D：Quality / Approval / Context operation panels&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-E/F：Reference Console integration + browser smoke baseline&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-G：用户显式确认的 patch apply/reject/publish&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-H：canvas / Inspector intent 到 patch proposal 桥接&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-I/J：Agent stateful assistant + governance baseline&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-K/L：Agent handoff + lifecycle / audit / recovery&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-M/N/O/P：evidence、canvas、proposal workflow、AgentTalk E2E&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-Q/R/S：executor design、production preflight、auth/tenant design&lt;br&gt;• V4.0-T/U/V/W/X/Y/Z：production follow-up designs、consolidation、final audit" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="590" x="100" y="1100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="gap" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFBEB;strokeColor=#F59E0B;align=left;spacingLeft=18;fontSize=15" value="当前剩余差距&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• 仍没有完整 AgentTalkWindow 状态机和真实 Agent executor&lt;br&gt;• Agent 仍不能自动 apply / reject / publish / approval.respond&lt;br&gt;• Handoff 已有 lifecycle / audit / recovery，但仍不是 executor&lt;br&gt;• Agent 仍不能 update context / emit business event / start workflow&lt;br&gt;• 仍没有完整低代码画布编辑器和 layout persistence&lt;br&gt;• 仍不是 complete Workflow Studio ready" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="590" x="805" y="1100" as="geometry" />
