        <mxCell id="target" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ECFDF5;strokeColor=#059669;align=left;spacingLeft=18;fontSize=15" value="V4.0-Z Final Audit Gate&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• 允许：governed dev/local Workflow Console + production readiness design gates ready for implementation review&lt;br&gt;• T/U/V/W：token、secret、observability、external app 设计合同&lt;br&gt;• X：production readiness consolidation&lt;br&gt;• Y：controlled executor implementation gate&lt;br&gt;• Z：final audit package&lt;br&gt;• 仍 no production-ready / no enterprise auth / no executor ready" vertex="1">
